column5: @ContactTypeDetails specifies the details of the contact's role or roles. If Part/@ContactType="Employee", then @ContactTypeDetails SHALL define the list of roles that the employee fills.
Identifier of the cost center that this Contact belongs to if Part/ @ContactType="Employee".
User ID of user, as specified when logging into the operating system or into the submitting application.
Communication channels such as phone number or email of the contact.
Company that this Contact is associated with.
